text: Miss World Philippines 2019, the 9th edition of the Miss World Philippines competition, was held at the Smart Araneta Coliseum, Quezon City, Philippines on September 15, 2019. Outgoing Miss World Philippines 2018 Katarina Sonja Rodriguez crowned her successor Michelle Marquez Dee as Miss World Philippines 2019 by the end of the event. The Miss World Philippines Organization crowned a new set of winners for 2019. Michelle Dee garnered the most coveted title of Miss World Philippines 2019, while five additional titleholders were also elected: Kelley Day as Miss Eco Philippines 2019, Maria Katrina Llegado as Reina Hispanoamericana Filipinas 2019, Isabelle de Leon as Miss Multinational Philippines 2019, Glyssa Leiann Perez as Miss Tourism Philippines 2019, and Vanessa-Mae Walters as Miss Teen Eco International Philippines 2019 and later was dethroned and replaced by Mary Daena Zaide Resurrecion to represent the Philippines at Miss Teen Eco International 2019.https://news.abs- cbn.com/life/07/09/19/beauty-queens-wanted-miss-world-ph-mutya-pilipinas-call- for-applicants == Results == ;Color keys * The contestant won in an International pageant. * The contestant was a Finalist/Runner-up in an International pageant. * The contestant was a Semi-Finalist in an International pageant. * The contestant assumed another title. * The contestant did not place. {| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size: 90%;" !width="280" style="background-color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|National Title !width="300" style="background-color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|Candidate !width="250" style="background-color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|International Placement |- | style="background:#FFFACD;" |Miss World Philippines 2019 |style="background:#FFFACD;" | * #21 - Michelle Dee !style="background:#FFFACD;" | Top 12 |- ||Miss Eco Philippines 2019 || * #24 Kelley Day !
